{{define "done"}}
<div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0;">
  <div class="icon-chip" style="width:3.5rem;height:3.5rem;border-radius:50%;background:rgb(var(--success) / .12);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="rgb(var(--success))" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <h2 class="t-h2" style="margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Install complete</h2>
  <p class="t-small" style="color:rgb(var(--muted));margin-bottom:1.5rem;max-width:26rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
    The wizard is locked. The panel pushed a self-bootstrap route to your
    first Caddy node, so the public address you entered now reverse-proxies
    back to this app - sign in there, not on this temporary URL.
  </p>

  {{if .Form.AppURL}}
  <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;text-align:left;background:rgb(var(--surface-2));border:1px solid rgb(var(--border));border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;" class="t-caption">
    <div><strong>Public panel URL:</strong> <a href="{{.Form.AppURL}}" style="color:rgb(var(--accent));text-decoration:underline;word-break:break-all;">{{.Form.AppURL}}</a></div>
    <div><strong>Before you sign in there:</strong> point a DNS A record for that hostname at your Caddy node's public IP, then wait one Let's Encrypt issuance cycle (~30s on first hit).</div>
    <div style="color:rgb(var(--muted));">If you forgot the IP or want to add more hosts, sign in via the local URL below first, then jump to /admin/hosts/new.</div>
  </div>
  {{end}}

  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:0.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    {{if .Form.AppURL}}
    <a href="{{.Form.AppURL}}/auth/login" class="r-btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;">
      Sign in at panel URL &rarr;
    </a>
    {{end}}
    <a href="/auth/login" class="r-btn-secondary" style="display:inline-block;">
      Sign in locally
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
{{end}}
